latestPosts.caption:
Cafe vlog featuring my Instax Square Link Printer ☕📸
There’s something extra special about turning cafe memories into prints on the spot and with the Instax Square Link, I can personalize each one with cute text, stickers, and even AR features right from the app.
Plus, with the Instax UP! app, I can scan and store all my prints digitally too, best of both worlds!
Every coffee deserves a memory, and now I get to keep mine forever 💛
